# PolarCraft Frontend Environment Variables

# API 配置 / API Configuration
# 本地开发时填写后端地址；单服务部署到 Render 时可留空，前端会自动使用同源 /api
# Set the backend origin for local development; leave blank for same-origin Render deploys
VITE_API_URL=

# PostHog 分析 / PostHog Analytics
# 在 PostHog 项目设置里复制 Project API Key
# Copy the Project API Key from your PostHog project settings
VITE_PUBLIC_POSTHOG_KEY=

# 可选：如果你的 PostHog 项目在欧盟区，填写 https://eu.i.posthog.com
# Optional: for EU region projects use https://eu.i.posthog.com
VITE_PUBLIC_POSTHOG_HOST=https://us.i.posthog.com

# 可选：是否开启会话录屏（true / false）
# Optional: enable session recordings (true / false)
VITE_PUBLIC_POSTHOG_SESSION_RECORDING=false

# 开发说明 / Development Notes:
# - 这些是 Vite 环境变量，必须以 VITE_ 开头才能在客户端代码中访问
# - These are Vite environment variables, must start with VITE_ to be accessible in client code
# - 在生产环境中，这些变量会在构建时被替换
# - In production, these variables are replaced at build time
